item.title: Need help to make a 525 Server
item.dc:creator: @durial12 durial12
item.description:
@durial12 wrote:

Firstly, you need to download a source.

To make yourself owner, I believe you have to get to your character file, then change the number next to rights (will be 0) to 2. Then compile and then run the server.

To get your server online, you can follow tutorials on this forum (or use google). There are hundreds of them so just look.

Durial
